reviewText: This weird grab-bag of wrestling matches from hither and hither -- that's right, they didn't even bother to go thither -- is a disappointment unless your requirements are infinitesimally minimal. In addition, the disc is marred by glitches that would make it hard to watch even if the matches themselves were more entertaining and/or outrageous. All that's outrageous is the notion of wasting money on this thing.
